{"tid":668064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★失業率創20年新低跌至2.8%","createTime":"2018-05-17T09:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T08:49:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"396ad80cee0509093c9359d69958edb1e3bbcd3d","tid":668064,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T09:33:40.000Z","msg":"本港失業率跌至20年新低水平！政府統計處今日（17日）公布的最新勞動人口統計數字，經季節性調整的失業率由今年1月至3月的2.9%，下降至2月至4月的2.8%。<br />\n勞福局局長羅致光表示，受經濟表現強勁所支持，勞工市場在今年2月至4月進一步趨緊，失業率微跌0.1個百分點至2.8%，為逾20年以來的最低水平。<br />\n至於就業不足率，在該兩段期間則保持不變，維持於1.0%的水平。失業人數則由今年1月至3月的112,100人，上升至2月至4月的112,900人，增加約800人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/189547/%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E7%8E%87%E5%89%B520%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%8E%E8%B7%8C%E8%87%B32-8-%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%A5%AD%E5%8F%8A%E8%88%87%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%92%8C%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD%E6%9C%80%E6%98%8E%E9%A1%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F189547%2F%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%258E%2587%25E5%2589%25B520%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25BD%258E%25E8%25B7%258C%25E8%2587%25B32-8-%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E5%2592%258C%25E6%2597%2585%25E9%2581%258A%25E7%259B%25B8%25E9%2597%259C%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2598%258E%25E9%25A1%25AF&d=j%2Fc0ea5WgjbMERNZizTXtDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=1a40a017\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/189547/%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E7%8E%87%E5%89%B520%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%8E%E8%B7%8C%E8%87%B32-8-%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%A5%AD%E5%8F%8A%E8%88%87%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%92%8C%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD%E6%9C%80%E6%98%8E%E9%A1%AF</a>"},{"pid":"ef70806fed4264a45f7f26ae2cdad71e6e68c261","tid":668064,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score"